Ways to express love

When it comes to expressing love, men and women seem to use different "languages." Men are often more direct, like a sudden gust of wind, fierce and swift. They might express their feelings by giving gifts or creating romantic dates. For example, on anniversaries, a man might carefully prepare an expensive gift or take his woman to a fancy restaurant for a romantic dinner, demonstrating his love through concrete actions.

